OL,3,CTwo men seriously injured in Kinallen
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FTwo men have been seriously injured
OL,7,Ffollowing a single car crash in Co
OL,8,FDown.
OL,10,FThe collision happened in the
OL,11,FKatesbridge Road area of Kinallen on
OL,12,FSaturday afternoon.
OL,14,FThe driver and passenger, aged 19 and
OL,15,F22, were taken to hospital for
OL,16,Ftreatment.
OL,18,FPolice have appealed for information
OL,19,Fand witnesses.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
