OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1780341071
OL,3,CTwo men seriously injured in Kinallen
OL,4,Ccrash
OL,6,FInspector Lawson said: "At
OL,7,Fapproximately 12.40pm on Saturday,
OL,8,F30th May police responded to a
OL,9,Fcollision involving a red Volkswagen
OL,10,FJetta in the Katesbridge Road area.
OL,12,F"Colleagues from the Northern Ireland
OL,13,FAmbulance Service attended, and the
OL,14,Fdriver and passenger, two men aged 19
OL,15,Fand 22, were both taken onward to
OL,16,Fhospital for treatment to injuries
OL,17,Fwhich are believed to be serious.
OL,19,F"The road which was closed for a time
OL,20,Fhas now fully reopened to road users."
